version_description: Other versions of this song are incorrect. Song has more minor chords and Gsus4 fits for the end.
These are all basic chords if you use a capo on the first fret.
This Chord Chart is set in a deeper key, for those users w/ a low vocal register. Also, correct lyrics.
The voicings of the chords have been modified to add extra feeling to the song, and uniqueness to each part.
Coldplay - Warning Sign Acoustic version (AOL live session 2003).
All of the 5 star versions of these songs were either not fully completed (Not every verse/ chorus had the chords) and some were done with the wrong Capo which made for the wrong chords too
